
nordvpn-update [-h] [-c country] [-u url] [-p protocol] [-d directory] [-a custom.conf]

Retrieves the NordVPN .ovpn configuration files for the specified
country and protocol and installs them to /etc/ovpn/.

Options:

 h, --help	display this help and exit
 c, --country	set server country (uk, us, fr, etc.)
		defaults to uk
 p, --protocol	communication protocol (udp, tcp)
		defaults to udp
 u, --url	server ovpn url
		defaults to https://downloads.nordcdn.com/configs/archives/servers/ovpn.zip
 d, --directory	set installation directory
		defaults to /etc/openvpn
 a, --append	path to custom configuration options appended to configuration
		defaults to /home/rhys/.nordvpn/custom.conf

